e Line Features]] || [[Jennifer Jason Leigh]], [[Alan Cumming]] (director/screenplay); [[Jennifer Jason Leigh]], [[Alan Cumming]], [[Kevin Kline]], [[John C. Reilly]], [[Jane Adams (actress)|Jane Adams]], [[Parker Posey]], [[Phoebe Cates]], [[Gwyneth Paltrow]], [[Denis O'Hare]], Mina Badie, [[John Benjamin Hickey]], [[Michael Panes]], [[Jennifer Beals]] || [[comedy film|Comedy]], [[drama film|Drama]] || [[Live action]]\n|-\n| ''[[Bride of the Wind]]'' || [[Paramount Classics]] || [[Bruce Beresford]] (director); Marilyn Levy (screenplay); [[Sarah Wynter]], [[Jonathan Pryce]], [[Vincent Perez]], [[Simon Verhoeven]], [[Gregor Seberg]], Dagmar Schwarz, Wolfgang Hubsch, [[August Schmolzer]], [[Johannes Silberschneider]], Hans Steunzer, Robert Herzl || [[Period film|Period]], [[Drama film|Drama]] || [[Live action]]\n|-\n| ''[[Evolution (2001 film)|Evolution]]'' || [[DreamWorks Pictures|DreamWorks]] / [[Columbia Pictures]] / [[The Montecito Picture Company]] || [[Ivan Reitman]] (director); [[David Diamond (screenwriter)|David Diamond]], [[David Weissman]], Don Jakoby (screenplay); [[David Duchovny]], [[Orlando Jones]], [[Seann William Scott]], [[Julianne Moore]], [[Ted Levine]], [[Ethan Suplee]], [[Ty Burrell]], [[Dan Aykroyd]], [[Michael Bower]], [[Pat Kilbane]], Katharine Towne, [[Gregory Itzin]], [[Stephanie Hodge]], [[Kyle Gass]], [[Sarah Silverman]], [[Richard Moll]], [[Tom Davis (comedian)|Tom Davis]], [[Jerry Trainor]], [[Miriam Flynn]], [[John Cho]], Caroline Reitman, Ashley Clark || [[science fiction film|Sci-Fi]], [[comedy film|Comedy]] || [[Live action]]\n|-\n| ''[[Swordfish (film)|Swordfish]]'' || [[Warner Bros. Pictures]] / [[Village Roadshow Pictures]] / <small>[[Silver Pictures]]</small> || [[Dominic Sena]] (director); [[Skip Woods]] (screenplay); [[John Travolta]], [[Hugh Jackman]], [[Halle Berry]], [[Don Cheadle]], [[Vinnie Jones]], [[Sam Shepard]], [[Drea de Matteo]], [[Rudolf Martin]], [[Zach Grenier]], [[Camryn Grimes]], [[Kirk B.R. Woller]], [[Carmen A