y Hopkins]], [[Anton Yelchin]], [[Hope Davis]], [[Mika Boorem]], [[David Morse (actor)|David Morse]], [[Deirdre O'Connell (actress)|Deirdre O'Connell]], [[Will Rothhaar]], [[Timothy Reifsnyder (actor)|Timmy Reifsnyder]], [[Alan Tudyk]], [[Tom Bower (actor)|Tom Bower]], [[Celia Weston]], [[Adam LeFevre]] || [[drama film|Drama]], [[Thriller film|Thriller]] || [[Live action]]\n|-\n| ''[[Zoolander]]'' || [[Paramount Pictures]] / [[Village Roadshow Pictures]] / [[VH1|VH1 Films]] || [[Ben Stiller]] (director); [[Drake Sather]], [[Ben Stiller]], [[John Hamburg]] (screenplay); [[Ben Stiller]], [[Owen Wilson]], [[Will Ferrell]], [[Christine Taylor]], [[Milla Jovovich]], [[Jerry Stiller]], [[David Duchovny]], [[Jon Voight]], [[Vince Vaughn]], [[Judah Friedlander]], [[Alexander Skarsgard]], [[Nathan Lee Graham]], [[Justin Theroux]], [[Andrew Wilson (actor)|Andrew Wilson]], [[John Vargas]], [[Jennifer Coolidge]], [[Tony Kanal]], [[Patton Oswalt]], Mason Webb, [[David Bowie]], [[Billy Zane]], [[Lance Bass]], [[Tyson Beckford]], [[Victoria Beckham]], [[Emma Bunton]], [[Stephen Dorff]], [[Shavo Odadjian]], [[Fred Durst]], [[Fabio Lanzoni|Fabio]], [[Tom Ford]], [[Cuba Gooding Jr.]], [[Theo Kogan]], [[Lukas Haas]], [[Tommy Hilfiger]], [[Paris Hilton]], [[Carmen Kass]], [[Heidi Klum]], [[Lenny Kravitz]], [[Karl Lagerfeld]], [[Lil' Kim]], [[Anne Meara]], [[Natalie Portman]], [[Frankie Rayder]], [[Mark Ronson]], [[Gavin Rossdale]], [[Winona Ryder]], [[Garry Shandling]], [[Christian Slater]], [[Gwen Stefani]], [[Donald Trump]], [[Melania Trump]], [[Donatella Versace]], [[Veronica Webb]], [[James Marsden]] || [[comedy film|Comedy]] || [[Live action]]\n|}\n\n*''[[The Return of Jafar]]'' (Theatrical release) - September 14, 2001\n\n===October\u2013December===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|+ \"align=bottom\" |\n! colspan=\"2\" | Opening\n! style=\"width:17%\"| Title\n! style=\"width:16%\"| Studio\n! Cast and crew\n! style=\"width:10%\"| Genre\n! style=\"width:8%\"|